  "instructions": [
    "Heat vegetable oil in a deep frying pan to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a bowl, mix together the Mars bars, plant-based milk, and cornstarch until well combined.",
    "Add in spices if using and mix to coat the Mars bars evenly.",
    "Form the Mars bar mixture into small patties or nuggets.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together the agemono batter mix and rice flour.",
    "Coat each Mars bar patty in the batter mix, pressing gently to adhere.",
    "Fry the battered Mars bar patties in the hot oil for 2-3 minutes on each side, until golden brown and crispy.",
    "Drain the patties on paper towels and garnish with fresh parsley."
